"庫存的批次/序號（進入倉庫庫存的\\ **最後一個**\\ 批次/序號）建立調撥。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/lifo.rst:16
msgid ""
