"For examples on how to configure specific shipping methods, refer to the "
"sections below."
msgstr "有關如何配置特定運送方式的範例，請參閱以下各節。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:82
msgid "Fixed price"
msgstr "固定價格"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:84
msgid ""
"To configure a shipping price that is the same for all orders, go "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Shipping Methods`. "
"Then, click :guilabel:`New`, and on the shipping method form, set "
"the :guilabel:`Provider` to the :guilabel:`Fixed Price` option. Selecting "
"this option makes the :guilabel:`Fixed Price` field become available, which "
"is where the fixed rate shipping amount is defined."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:90
msgid ""
"To enable free shipping if the amount of the order exceeds a specified "
"amount, check the box :guilabel:`Free if order amount is above` and fill in "
"the amount."
msgstr ""
"若要在訂單金額超過指定金額時啟用免費運送，請勾選\\ :guilabel:`訂單金額超過時"
"免費`\\ 核取方塊並填入金額。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:94
msgid ""
"To set up `$20` flat-rate shipping that becomes free if the customer spends "
"over `$100`, fill in the following fields:"
msgstr ""
"若要設定固定費率運費為 `$20`，並在客戶消費超過 `$100` 時變為免費，請填寫以下"
"欄位："

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:97
msgid ":guilabel:`Shipping Method`: `Flat-rate shipping`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:98
msgid ":guilabel:`Provider`: :guilabel:`Fixed Price`"
msgstr "\\ :guilabel:`供應商`\\ ：\\ :guilabel:`固定價格`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:99
msgid ":guilabel:`Fixed Price`: `$20.00`"
msgstr "\\ :guilabel:`固定價格`\\ ：`$20.00`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:100
msgid ":guilabel:`Free if order amount is above`: `$100.00`"
msgstr "\\ :guilabel:`訂單金額超過時免費`\\ ：`$100.00`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:101
msgid ":guilabel:`Delivery Product`: `[SHIP] Flat`"
msgstr "\\ :guilabel:`運送產品`\\ ：`[SHIP] Flat`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:0
msgid "Example of filling out a shipping method."
msgstr "填寫運送方式的範例。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:109
msgid "Based on rules"
msgstr "根據規則"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:111
msgid ""
"To calculate the price of shipping based on pricing rules, set "
"the :guilabel:`Provider` field to the :guilabel:`Based on Rules` option. "
"Optionally, adjust :guilabel:`Margin on Rate` and :guilabel:`Additional "
"margin` to include additional shipping costs."
msgstr ""
"若要根據定價規則計算運費，請將\\ :guilabel:`供應商`\\ 欄位設為\\ :guilabel:`"
"根據規則`\\ 選項。您可選擇調整\\ :guilabel:`費率利潤`\\ 和\\ :guilabel:`額外"
"利潤`\\ ，以納入額外的運送成本。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:116
msgid "Create pricing rules"
msgstr "建立定價規則"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:118
msgid ""
"Navigate to the :guilabel:`Pricing` tab and click :guilabel:`Add a line`. "
"Doing so opens the :guilabel:`Create Pricing Rules` window, where "
"the :guilabel:`Condition` related to the product weight, volume, price, or "
"quantity is compared to a defined amount to calculate "
"the :guilabel:`Delivery Cost`."
msgstr ""
"導覽至\\ :guilabel:`定價`\\ 分頁並按一下\\ :guilabel:`加入資料行`\\ 。這將開"
"啟\\ :guilabel:`建立定價規則`\\ 視窗，其中與產品重量、體積、價格或數量相關的"
"\\ :guilabel:`條件`\\ 將與定義的金額進行比較，以計算\\ :guilabel:`運送成本"
"`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:123
msgid ""
"Once finished, click either :guilabel:`Save & New` to add another rule, "
"or :guilabel:`Save & Close`."
msgstr ""
"完成後，按一下\\ :guilabel:`儲存並新增`\\ 以加入另一條規則，或按一下"
"\\ :guilabel:`儲存並關閉`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:126
msgid ""
"To charge customers $20 in shipping for orders with five or fewer products, "
"set the :guilabel:`Condition` to `Quantity <= 5.00`, and "
"the :guilabel:`Delivery Cost` to `$20`."
msgstr ""
"若要針對包含五件或更少產品的訂單向客戶收取 $20 運費，請將\\ :guilabel:`條件"
"`\\ 設為 `數量 <= 5.00`，並將\\ :guilabel:`運送成本`\\ 設為 `$20`。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:0
msgid ""
"Display window to add a pricing rule. Set a condition and delivery cost."
msgstr "顯示加入定價規則的視窗。設定條件和運送成本。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:132
msgid ""
"To restrict shipping to specific destinations on the eCommerce website, in "
"the shipping method form, navigate to the :guilabel:`Destination "
"Availability` tab and define the :guilabel:`Countries`, :guilabel:`States`, "
"and :guilabel:`Zip Prefixes`. Leave these fields empty if all locations "
"apply."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:137
msgid "Calculate delivery cost"
msgstr "計算運送成本"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:139
msgid ""
"Shipping cost is the :guilabel:`Delivery cost` specified in the rule that "
"satisfies the :guilabel:`Condition`, plus any extra charges from "
"the :guilabel:`Margin on rate` and :guilabel:`Additional margin`."
