msgstr ""
"作為臨時解決方案，:doc:`Sendcloud 整合 <sendcloud_shipping>`\\ 也支援聯邦快遞"
"服務。若要請求進一步協助，請\\ `提交支援工單 <https://www.odoo.com/help>`_。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex.rst:21
