"`\\ 。按一下\\ :guilabel:`確定`\\ 以關閉\\ :guilabel:`檢視中繼資料`\\ 彈出視"
"窗。"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/zebra.rst:None
